We sell or share your Device, Internet and Network Activity Information, and Online Identifiers with third parties for targeted advertising.
We also use this information to:
Personalize your experience with us, including promotional communications sent through email and text messages;
Provide access to our Services in a form that can be viewed most easily from your device;
Determine the general geographic region from which you are accessing the Services, using your IP Address, which allows us to present appropriate content and inform you of special rules or rights that may apply to people in your jurisdiction;
Review statistical information about the use of the systems in order to improve their design and functionality, to understand how they are used, and to assist us with resolving questions;
Recognize you, your device or your browser when you use our services so that we can facilitate navigation and display information more effectively; and
Track responses to our e-mails and advertisements.
Inform you about new products, features, updates, and special promotions, including third-party offers or products we think you might find interesting; and
Serve you ads about products and offers.
