D. For all Users of our Services
In all instances, we may use all of the categories of Personal Information noted above as we believe necessary:
to verify your identity or determine your eligibility for some of our products, services, and promotions. For example, this may include verifying your age, date of birth, and state of residence;
if we determine a policy violation has occurred, to enforce our rights, or to enforce agreements;
to protect against unauthorized access to our systems or other inappropriate use of our Services, including protecting the safety of our company, our Services, consumers who use our Services, and others;
to comply with laws, regulations, court orders and subpoenas or similar requests for information by authorities;
to perform audits;
to contact you about Services or policy updates;
for research and analytics, including to identify usage trends, and to improve and update our products and services;
to assist us in fraud prevention or investigation, all on the basis of our legitimate interest in the continuation of our commercial activities and the protection of our rights; and
for purposes otherwise permitted by law or as we may notify you and obtain your consent.
